<br />I agree. I don't really know why, but I found the music in Casltevania III sounds more "limpid". In Akumajo Densetsu III, they used more channels for Chrous and echo effects, but not for actually more channels. They just rewired all triangle stuff on the saw wave channel. The advantage is that the VRC6 saw vave has volume control. But I still prefer Castlevania III.
